com.informatica.mdm.bpm.idd

Class IDDTaskData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.informatica.mdm.bpm.idd.IDDTaskData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITaskData

    public class IDDTaskData
extends Object
implements ITaskData
    Represents task data in IDD and implements the ITaskData interface. The task records set in this class are of type MDMTaskRecord. This is used by IDD to pass task related data to the BPM adapters for various operations.
    See Also:
    MDMTaskRecord, ITaskData
